## Additional Terms for Myanmar Context

This software is specifically designed for emergency preparedness and public safety 
in Myanmar. The developers encourage responsible use of this system for:

- Emergency alert distribution
- Public safety communications
- Disaster preparedness
- Community protection

The software should not be used for:
- Spreading false information
- Political propaganda
- Commercial spam
- Any illegal activities

For questions about appropriate use, please contact: team@thatialert.com